data.description: RANCHER with WOW factor! Offering 1497 sq ft over open floor plan The Freeport is a thoughtfully designed home with four bedrooms and two full bathrooms. This split design places the owner's suite separate from the secondary bedrooms. The owner's suite features a walk-in closet and en suite full bath. The fourth bedroom is also separate from the second and third bedrooms, providing a great flex room to use as a home office or game room. The kitchen island looks out over the spacious great room, and has undermount sink built in for easy food preparation. Every Freeport home includes D.R. Horton's Home is Connected® package, an industry leading suite of smart home products. Included decorator features, upgraded cabinets, granite countertops and vanity tops, washer/ dryer, window blinds, 2 car garage and so much more. The Links at Gettysburg community features acclaimed golf, tennis, swimming pool, community clubhouse, sport court, tot lot, and event venue. Set your tour today! *Photos are of similar home, and are for viewing purposes only*
